These are Puzzles for 7x3 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-1::.
3 different pets are kept: fish, hamster, cat
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: april, december, november
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, game, chaman
The people have 3 different jobs:  accountant, designer, mechanic
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: country, d&b, dubstep
There are 3 different favourite colors: pink, red, mauve
The people use 3 different means of transport: scooter, subway, quad-bike
 1. the person driving the scooter is the person who likes red##1
 2. the person driving the quad-bike is the mechanic##1
 3. the owner of the cat is between the person who likes mauve and the owner of the hamster##2
 4. the fan of d&b is on the left of the person who likes pink##1
 5. the designer is the person who's birthday is in november##1
 6. the chaman-smoker is the person who likes pink##1
 7. the chaman-smoker is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 8. the person driving the subway is on the left of the fan of country##1
 9. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the designer##1
10. the game-smoker is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |       3       |
| Pet      | hamster    | cat   | fish           |
| Birthday          | december       | november    | april         |
| Cigar         | game    | chaman  | tiparillo        |
| Job           | accountant | designer   | mechanic      |
| Music-Genre   | d&b        | dubstep    | country       |
| Color   | red     | pink  | mauve       |
| Transport         | scooter     | subway | quad-bike |

