.:: Puzzle 7x3-Level-2-2::.
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: august, october, may
There 3 different types of food: apricot, nectarine, pear
House: ranch-style, colonial, townhouse
There are 3 different favourite colors: turquise, coral, chestnut
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: oliveros, bolivar, baccarat
3 different pets are kept: dog, horse, pony
3 different games are played: monopoly, chess, poker
 1. the owner of the pony is the bolivar-smoker##1
 2. the owner of the pony is the townhouse house##1
 3. the townhouse house is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 4. the person playing monopoly is between the person who's birthday is in october and the person who's birthday is in august##2
 5. the baccarat-smoker is on the far left##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in october is the person who likes turquise##1
 7. the person who likes coral is on the left of the person playing poker##1
 8. the person eating apricot is the ranch-style house##1
 9. the townhouse house is on the right of the person who likes chestnut##1
10. the owner of the pony is on the left of the person eating pear##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |       3       |
| Birthday      | august   | may    | october         |
| Food          | apricot    | nectarine | pear          |
| House   | ranch-style  | townhouse  | colonial     |
| Color   | chestnut       | coral      | turquise         |
| Cigar   | baccarat      | bolivar   | oliveros    |
| Pet           | dog        | pony      | horse         |
| Game         | chess | monopoly  | poker |

