The people use 3 different means of transport: roller, trike, taxi
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: tiparillo, pall-mall, blend
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: zinnia, sunflower, marigold
There are 3 different favourite colors: purple, ebony, blood-red
 1. the person drinking hot-chocolate is the person who growssunflower##1
 2. the blend-smoker is the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
 3. the person watching adventure movies is the person drinking iced-tea##1
 4. the person watching satire movies is the person who growssunflower##1
 5. the person who likes ebony is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
 6. the person watching satire movies is on the left of the person who likes blood-red##1
 7. the person who's hobby is skydiving is between the pall-mall-smoker and the person driving the taxi##2
 8. the pall-mall-smoker is on the left of the person driving the roller##1
 9. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who likes purple##1
10. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the person drinking hot-chocolate##1
11. the pall-mall-smoker is the person drinking iced-tea##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |
