There 3 different types of food: broccoli, strawberry, grapes
The people have 3 different jobs:  musician, security-guard, social-worker
There are 3 different favourite colors: coral, blood-red, light-blue
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: june, may, january
There are 3 different nationalities: dutch, egyptian, malaysian
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: tulip, zinnia, dahlia
 1. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person playing go##1
 2. the person playing bridge is the malaysian##1
 3. the person who growsdahlia is on the left of the person who likes light-blue##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
 5. the person who's birthday is in june is between the person who likes blood-red and the person playing bridge##2
 6. the person playing go is on the right of the person eating broccoli##1
 7. the person who's birthday is in june is the person eating grapes##1
 8. the musician is the person who growsdahlia##1
 9. the person playing go is between the musician and the social-worker##2
10. the malaysian is on the left of the egyptian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |       2        |       3       |
| Game      | bridge | go           | monopoly      |
| Food         | broccoli       | grapes         | strawberry       |
| Job           | musician    | security-guard | social-worker |
