 4. the person who likes yellow is on the far right##1
 5. the townhouse house is between the cape-cod house and the person who's birthday is in april##2
 6. the townhouse house is between the ranch-style house and the person traveling to hannover##2
 7. the person driving the bike is between the french and the person who likes white##2
 8. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 9. the journalist is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
10. the engineer is the french##1

.:: Answer ::.
