House: modern, farmhouse, futuristic
City: rome, paris, hamburg
The people use 3 different means of transport: subway, taxi, van
 1. the person traveling to hamburg is in the middle##1
 2. the fan of gospel is in the middle##1
 3. the polish is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
 4. the person who growssunflower is the bartender##1
 5. the person driving the subway is on the right of the polish##1
 6. the futuristic house is on the left of the bartender##1
 7. the person driving the van is between the fan of blues and the american##2
 8. the videographer is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 9. the bartender is the person driving the subway##1
10. the futuristic house is on the left of the farmhouse house##1
11. the person driving the subway is the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |    3     |
| Music-Genre      | blues | gospel      | classical      |
| Flower         | amaryllis     | dahlia     | sunflower  |
| Job   | electrician | videographer  | bartender |
| Nationality   | indonesian  | polish     | american |
| House           | modern        | futuristic | farmhouse     |
| City         | rome    | hamburg | paris   |
| Transport     | taxi        | van        | subway   |

