6. the person who growsmarigold is on the right of the swisher-smoker##1
7. the person who's sport is surfing is on the right of the person who's birthday is in july##1
8. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person who's birthday is in august##1
9. the person traveling to marchsy is on the left of the american##1

.:: Answer ::.
