The people have 3 different jobs:  dressmaker, fisherman, nurse
The people have 3 different hobbies: gardening, puzzles, photography
City: edinburgh, miami, venice
3 different games are played: mah-jongg, go, scrabble
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: may, june, april
1. the dunhill-smoker is the person eating zucchini##1
2. the person who's birthday is in april is the person playing mah-jongg##1
3. the dressmaker is between the prince-smoker and the person traveling to venice##2
4. the person who's hobby is gardening is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
5. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
6. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person who's birthday is in april##1
7. the fisherman is the person eating broccoli##1
8. the person traveling to venice is on the left of the person traveling to edinburgh##1
9. the person who's hobby is puzzles is between the person eating broccoli and the person who's birthday is in may##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |
| Cigar      | dannemann    | dunhill       | prince      |
| Food          | broccoli   | zucchini   | spinach  |
| Job           | fisherman  | dressmaker | nurse    |
| Hobby   | gardening   | puzzles     | photography  |
| City           | venice     | edinburgh        | miami |
| Game         | go | mah-jongg   | scrabble  |
| Birthday     | june    | april     | may      |

 